description: When reflecting on the wonderful offerings of beautiful Sacramento, Rudy’s Hideaway must instantly come to mind. With their signature friendly service and delicious seafood dishes, this fun family-run restaurant has been a local favorite (and not to mention, landmark) since all the way back in 1972. Now they’re bringing their same famously tasty food straight to you, thanks to Rudy’s On the Roll. This big checkered truck is treating the foodies of the streets, festivals, events, etc... to a full Rudy’s experience, complete with high-quality ingredients, delightfully scrumptious seafood, and wide warm smiles. With a menu that includes award-winning creamy Boston Clam Chowder, tangy Cajun Shrimp Tacos, succulent Lobster Rolls, and much more, Rudy’s On the Roll is totally the truck to choose for your next party or meal!
name: Rudy's On the Roll
